_sText:
AIM_MIDDLE_GLASS

Map provided by iCemaTProductions.

INFO:
You'll start with a knife, hit the single button beside the box, everytime a loud alert goes on, you "Reach new lvl" in weapon, other words - you can choose a higher number on the otherside of the box, higher Number means better weapon.

The black/Gray button in the middle of the glass, will activate the wall with Graffiti on, in the middle.. If only the one team press it, the wall will take 30 secs to start open, and if both of the team have pressed it, it will open in 3 secs, while in 1,5 secs the Metal walls will begin moving to each side with different speeds :)

Have fun, and have a nice Aim Fight! :)

Kind regards,
iCe
